<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Airbnb Audit</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <main class="container">
    <section class="hero">
     <!-- <h1>Why is your Airbnb not getting enough bookings?</h1> -->
	  <h1>¿Por qué tu Airbnb no recibe reservas?</h1>
      <p>
      <!--  Get a clear manual audit of your listing with practical fixes:
        photo order, title, pricing positioning, and conversion issues.
		<br> -->
		Analizamos tu anuncio y te decimos qué está frenando tus reservas: portada, orden de fotos, título, precio y errores clave...
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h2>Request your audit</h2>
      <h2>Quiero mi análisis</h2>

      <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="error"><%= error %></div>
      <% } %>

      <form method="POST" action="/submit" class="form">
        <label>
          Name *
          <input type="text" name="name" value="<%= formData.name %>" required />
        </label>

        <label>
          Email *
          <input type="email" name="email" value="<%= formData.email %>" required />
        </label>

        <label>
          Airbnb listing URL *
          <input
            type="url"
            name="airbnb_url"
            placeholder="https://www.airbnb.com/rooms/..."
            value="<%= formData.airbnb_url %>"
            required
          />
        </label>

        <label>
          Notes
          <textarea
            name="notes"
            rows="4"
            placeholder="Anything specific you want reviewed?"
          ><%= formData.notes %></textarea>
        </label>

       <!-- <button type="submit">Send request</button> -->
		<button type="submit">Solicita tu análisis</button>
      </form>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
